Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:50.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:02:01.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:08.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:16.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:22.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:26.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:36.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:43.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:49.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:03:01.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:09.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:50.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能让你忘却伤痛 我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言语的她 默然低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:02:01.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任凭泪水洗刷着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:08.91,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延着冻结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:16.08,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛这无可喘息的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:22.65,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:26.25,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这可悲的理由束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.22,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:36.79,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水的彼岸 那闪耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:43.48,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狭小的窗口中 满眼是往昔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:49.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然无法像鸟儿一样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:03:01.72,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为让悲伤永远铭记于心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:09.01,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了忘却而闭目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:10.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:26.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:32.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:36.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:45.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:49.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:51.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:56.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:02.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:07.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:13.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:20.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:25.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:10.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵随风起舞 如同雨水滋润大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.11,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这个世界如此紧密不分 如此活泼生机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:26.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}却为何人们要互相伤害 为何离别会突然降临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:32.31,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遥远的地方 你总是会活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:36.63,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份温柔的笑颜依旧映在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:45.79,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}拥抱着你的碎片 刺痛着我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:49.57,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相连 因为我坚信 会再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:51.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:56.88,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:02.28,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:07.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:13.15,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:20.24,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:25.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永远不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 伊奥利亚的计划就全归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意识和维塔直接连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体仅仅是容器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到事情 我可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是比你们更上位种的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的先生们好像大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该我出场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 A-LAWS的旗舰被击落了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 切断敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队 集中攻击舰队中央
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就交给我吧 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吝惜弹药 持续攻击联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方舰队逐渐被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个战术…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩 集中攻击正面中央舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样突破敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam专心防卫母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 Gundam专心防卫母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的通信?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玛奈金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 久篠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯蒂·玛奈金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了对A-LAWS进行判决而利用你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗结束后 会再度追究你们的罪责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全部对 立刻采取回避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了 攻击要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥之光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方传来强能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才那道强烈的光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始第二发扫射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-DRIVE交换作业 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学迷彩 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各人报告受害状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 右舷损伤 轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON运输舰1艘沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS被击毁20机以上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS舰队貌似开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…那帮家伙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地型外宇宙航行母舰「天行者」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚在两个多世纪之前就预料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与未知种族的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-DRIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘舰就是人类的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人类从灭亡中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是方舟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告各舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始 我们天行者将进攻敌大型母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并夺回那里的量子演算系统「维塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 对之前帮助我们的诸位表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并对战死者表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 托勒密驶向敌方母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 航向修正为敌方母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回维塔 最低限度也要让敌方母舰沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了即将到来的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们对引起世界变革的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将世界从变革者的支配中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度改变这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场 最大展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终任务 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将不断探查侵入路线并前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机 击破炮台确保侵入路线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打出一条侵入路线来 TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型炮塔捕捉到我方位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 没完没了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种程度!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得挺不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没轮到我们出场么～?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GAGA部队就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们请作为我的皇牌吧 希林格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入路线上的敌方粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,57%排除的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新的MS部队来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新型机么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还那么多!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种形状… 难道说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭在自己开发的技术手里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者组织
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是TRANS-AM!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种数量!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS 直冲着这里过来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是自杀式兵器!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中在右舷炮击!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎… 怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 侵入地点到了么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把舰体当盾牌也要守住啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让它被击落!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON! 凯蒂!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干些什么 久篠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把任务完成!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷后方! 敌机出现!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着我家大佐~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想出手~~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特利库!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了 凯蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特利库!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船用的入港口!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用TRANS-AM一口气加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要冲进去了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场在舰首集中展开!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 着舰的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer Arios 开始防卫托勒密号!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始扫描敌方母舰构造 搜索维塔!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去0 Gundam那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定战术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开侵入敌方母舰!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算侵入进内部 利用MS进行接近战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也打算把维塔夺回去么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的自走机械人来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS也来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁全部隔离墙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 伊恩 准备应战!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要侵入了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想进去 Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部机体是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部机体是… 老哥的…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗! Rifle Bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狭窄成这样子 TRANS-AM也没得用!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自走机械人突破了隔壁 侵入进来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现维塔的位置了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置传输给机师们!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 菲露特!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正角登场了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们继续肆意妄为了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来妨碍我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦 瑞法芙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然战争 就得玩近身啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再杀你一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 Gundam先生哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子残量已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!来联接!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向舰桥的隔壁被突破了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定战术对应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会守住 这次一定!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久篠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强到这个地步!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是搅乱世界的罪恶!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要干掉你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够得到幸福吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠战斗胜利得到的什么未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的未来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们相互的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能把未来构筑起来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去支援哈勒维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 难道是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类正在被考验着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毁灭 还是再生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是由你来决定那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.31,0:23:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚·爱德!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在激斗依然继续 生命不断陨落之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser的闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告了新的世界的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BEYOND
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.38,0:24:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 成为革新者


